00:02:02.440 --> 00:02:04.230
5 plus 6 is 11.

00:02:04.230 --> 00:02:09.130
If there were more places here,
we would carry the 1 in

00:02:09.130 --> 00:02:10.030
the tens place.

00:02:10.030 --> 00:02:13.230
But there isn't, so you can
just write an 11 here.

00:02:13.230 --> 00:02:16.380
And so we are left with-- put
