00:02:32.830 --> 00:02:34.780
So it allows you to do things
in your head a little bit

00:02:34.780 --> 00:02:38.550
easier when you round, and then
you estimate the sum of

00:02:38.550 --> 00:02:40.570
the rounded numbers.

